posts.post_content:
A rare early RPPC of New York Highlander Jimmy Williams circa 1906.  This image was likely taken in Spring Training and is on an undivided (pre-early 1907) Velox postcard back.  The card measures 4.5 x 5.4 and is slightly trimmed.

$650 PPFF shipped.
